reviews: Room service has some of problem they allow spaghetti but no penne in pasta and somemof guy don't have good attitude. But receptionist joy is so good nature helping nature.

reviews: The hotel is clean, beautiful view, has a private beach, breakfast has a variety of choices, delicious, but when entering the room is a bit difficult. You have to take a tram or wait for a staff member to drive you up to pick you up.
